This paper is related to natural language processing, specifically dependency parsing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of supertag features also involves machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves improving the accuracy of dependency parsing, which could be related to neural networks (cs.NE) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as well.
